snippet.title: Level Devil Walkthrough
snippet.description:

00:47 - Level 2
01:45 - Level 3
02:37 - Level 4
03:25 - Level 5
04:15 - Level 6
05:13 - Level 7
06:14 - Level 8
07:28 - Level 9
08:34 - Level 10
09:44 - Level 11
10:55 - Level 12
12:41 - Level 13
13:43 - Level 14
15:41 - Level 15
17:15 - Level 16
Level Devil is a platformer with a mean twist. The goal is simple. reach the door at the end of the level to win, but it's not as easy as it might seem... Holes can appear out of nowhere, spikes can move unexpectedly and ceilings can fall on you as you go through the many different flat. One wrong step and it's game over.
You can play the game:
https://poki.com/gr/g/level-devil#utm_source=redirect-en-el
